      • run

        public void run(int idx,
                boolean checkCurrentParagraph)
         throws IOException
        Parameters:
        idx - paragraph index
        checkCurrentParagraph - check whether you call this run method in the current paragraph. Set it to false only when you are sure you are not invoking this method to run current paragraph. Otherwise you would run current paragraph in infinite loop.
        Throws:
        IOException
